    <h2><a href="articles/no-more-blogging">No more blogging</a></h2>
    <div class="variables">
    <div class="date">@date=2009-11-30</div>
    <div class="tags">@tags=<a href="tags/constantsun-blogger-post">constantsun-blogger-post</a>, <a href="tags/blogging">blogging</a>, <a href="tags/editthisinfo">editthisinfo</a></div>
    </div>
    <article>
        <p>I created a google group here:</p>
<p><a href="http://groups.google.com/group/editthisinfo">http://groups.google.com/group/editthisinfo</a></p>
<p>from now on status messages and updates will be posted there. A blog is very much a one way form of communication, and I feel it goes against the collaborative nature of a wiki service. This group will be where problems and enhancements will be discussed.</p>
<p>If you are simply requesting a feature be added to editthis.info, please use the uservoice page:
<a href="http://editthis.uservoice.com/pages/35672-feature-requests">http://editthis.uservoice.com/pages/35672-feature-requests</a></p>

    </article>
    
